      <title>问答：土耳其央行行长谈论指导方针和通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/q-a-turkish-central-bank-governor-fatih-karahan-talks-rates-guidance-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行行长法提赫·卡拉汉周四在伊斯坦布尔接受彭博社采访，谈到了货币当局的前瞻性指引、通胀前景、储备、里拉流动性和掉期监管。为清晰起见，问题和答案经过了轻微编辑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/q-a-turkish-central-bank-governor-fatih-karahan-talks-rates-guidance-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其央行行长希望消除提前降息的传言</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/turkish-central-bank-head-wants-to-banish-talk-of-early-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行行长向担心过早放松政策的外国投资者发出了迄今为止最强烈​​的信息，称他希望确保今年以后能够实现通胀目标，然后再讨论降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/turkish-central-bank-head-wants-to-banish-talk-of-early-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 10:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
