      <title>需求低迷致中国信贷增长创历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/china-s-credit-growth-misses-expectations-as-demand-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国 6 月份信贷增长创下历史新低，凸显出借贷需求低迷，并促使一份由央行支持的出版物淡化对经济疲软的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-12/china-s-credit-growth-misses-expectations-as-demand-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jul 2024 09:05:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
